------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Repository Intelligence

Before creating an API ask

Does an API already exist?

Can an existing endpoint evolve?

Does another bounded context own this capability?

Does another plugin already expose it?

Would this duplicate an existing contract?

Search the repository before generating APIs.

