------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Repository Intelligence

Before creating

Endpoint

DTO

Validator

Mapper

Search the repository.

Reuse existing contracts whenever possible.

Avoid duplicate endpoints.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Review Checklist

Before implementation verify

✓ Correct Resource

✓ Correct HTTP Method

✓ DTO Used

✓ Validation Layered

✓ Status Codes Correct

✓ Pagination Defined

✓ Filtering Supported

✓ Version Defined

